y to provide a polished and high-fidelity presentation. Ultimately, I'll leverage actual project data, rather than simulated metrics.\n\n\n**Examining Project Data**\n\nI'm now closely examining the project data. I've noted three distinct entries: \"Global Retail Real-Time Audit Ring,\" \"Sovereign Logistics AI Route Optimizer,\" and \"Federal Treasury Multi-Enclave Ledger.\" I'm reviewing attributes such as phase, status, and owner. I'm taking note of the different `enclaveType` values (AMD SEV-SNP and AWS Nitro Enclave), which will be important for system architecture considerations. I'm focusing on parsing `desc` to understand key features of each project.\n\n\n**Defining Project Details Map**\n\nI'm now thinking about how to handle specific project IDs on the detail page. I am going to define a map to handle these, focusing on displaying a premium and customized layout for projects listed. I'll need to define how to handle new projects with the fallback to a default structure.\n\n\n**Implementing Project Details Page**\n\nI'm now fully immersed in building the `AdminProjectDetailPage`. Using the ID parameters feels extremely effective, and I'm designing the page as a highly structured view with tabs, graphics, and interactive elements. It satisfies all task requirements, ensuring a premium design without altering the landing page or introducing extraneous backend features. The route is explicit, with frontend-only mock states, and I will ensure the UI is fully responsive and accessible.\n\n\n**Listing Page Imports**\n\nI'm now outlining necessary imports for the `AdminProjectDetailPage`. I plan to include React and `useState` for state management, along with `useParams` and `useRouter` for route parameter retrieval. I'll import `Link` from `next/link` for navigation and a series of `lucide-react` icons for a rich UI.\n\n\n**Visualizing Project Data**\n\nI'm now integrating new project data points into the project detail page. I'm focusing on \"ISOLATION PROTOCOL,\" \"SLA RISK LEVEL,\" and \"TEAMS & CLEARANCE\" to provide key project context. I'm also planning a five-phase, interactive timeline that will highlight the current phase and progress of each project, using interactive visuals.\n\n\n**Designing Security Application**\n\nI'm now focusing on a security application with two key tabs. Tab two will list five security rules, with their status indicated. Tab three will focus on ephemeral resource allocations. The right column will hold a quick actions panel with telemetry controls and re-attestation buttons, as well as deliverer and ownership details.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-27T05:58:17.790Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"j93zwzw0","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/app/admin/projects/[id]/page.tsx","new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React, { useState, useEffect } from \"react\";\nimport { useParams, useRouter } from \"next/navigation\";\nimport Link from \"next/link\";\nimport { \n  ArrowLeft, Cpu, ShieldCheck, Activity, Clock, User, Briefcase, \n  Layers, Network, CheckCircle2, AlertTriangle, Server, Terminal, \n  Sliders, Lock, RefreshCw, Play, Square, Settings, ExternalLink, ShieldAlert\n} from \"lucide-react\";\n\ninterface AdminProject {\n  id: string;\n  name: string;\n  client: string;\n  phase: string;\n  status: string;\n  owner: string;\n  nodesCount: number;\n  enclaveType: string;\n  desc: string;\n  lastUpdated: string;\n}\n\nconst PROJECTS_REGISTRY: Record<string, AdminProject> = {\n  \"PROJ-201\": {\n    id: \"PROJ-201\",\n    name: \"Apex Sovereign Multi-Agent Lattice\",\n    client: \"Apex Sovereign Group\",\n    phase: \"Phase V: Production-Live\",\n    status: \"On Track\",\n    owner: \"Dr. Sarah Vance\",\n    nodesCount: 8,\n    enclaveType: \"Intel SGX\",\n    desc: \"High-throughput isolated core loop with secure localized kernel telemetry and dual-layer TLS 1.3 socket.\",\n    lastUpdated: \"2026-06-27T15:20:00Z\"\n  },\n  \"PROJ-202\": {\n    id: \"PROJ-202\",\n    name: \"Global Retail Real-Time Audit Ring\",\n    client: \"Global Retail Enclave\",\n    phase: \"Phase IV: User Acceptance Testing\",\n    status: \"At Risk\",\n    owner: \"Alexander Mercer\",\n    nodesCount: 5,\n    enclaveType: \"AMD SEV-SNP\",\n    desc: \"Continuous model alignment sandbox simulating extreme load, prompt injections, and runtime governance audits.\",\n    lastUpdated: \"2026-06-27T14:10:00Z\"\n  },\n  \"PROJ-203\": {\n    id: \"PROJ-203\",\n    name: \"Sovereign Logistics AI Route Optimizer\",\n    client: \"Sovereign Logistics Unit\",\n    phase: \"Phase III: Agent Alignment\",\n    status: \"Paused\",\n    owner: \"Marcus Vance\",\n    nodesCount: 4,\n    enclaveType: \"AWS Nitro Enclave\",\n    desc: \"Airgapped telemetry network running geological route optimizations inside ephemeral containerized enclaves.\",\n    lastUpdated: \"2026-06-26T18:05:00Z\"\n  },\n  \"PROJ-204\": {\n    id: \"PROJ-204\",\n    name: \"Federal Treasury Multi-Enclave Ledger\",\n    client: \"Federal Treasury Division\",\n    phase: \"Phase II: Sandbox Provisioning\",\n    status: \"Delayed\",\n    owner: \"Evelyn Carter\",\n    nodesCount: 12,\n    enclaveType: \"Intel SGX\",\n    desc: \"NIST-compliant hardware enclave isolating state estimation and cryptographic treasury signatures from host execution.\",\n    lastUpdated: \"2026-06-27T09:30:00Z\"\n  },\n  \"PROJ-205\": {\n    id: \"PROJ-205\",\n    name: \"National Health Secure Diagnostics Loop\",\n    client: \"National Health Enclave\",\n    phase: \"Phase I: Planning\",\n    status: \"On Track\",\n    owner: \"Auditor Jenkins\",\n    nodesCount: 3,\n    enclaveType: \"AMD SEV-SNP\",\n    desc: \"Zero-Trust medical agent handshake validating eBPF kernel event streams on medical imaging diagnostic models.\",\n    lastUpdated: \"2026-06-27T11:45:00Z\"\n  }\n};\n\nconst PHASES_LIST = [\n  \"Phase I: Planning\",\n  \"Phase II: Sandbox Provisioning\",\n  \"Phase III: Agent Alignment\",\n  \"Phase IV: User Acceptance Testing\",\n  \"Phase V: Production-Live\"\n];\n\nexport default function AdminProjectDetailPage() {\n  const router = useRouter();\n  const { id } = useParams();\n  const projectId = typeof id === \"string\" ? id : \"PROJ-201\";\n\n  // Fallback if the user created a new project ID not in current static record\n  const project: AdminProject = PROJECTS_REGISTRY[projectId] || {\n    id: projectId,\n    name: \"Dynamic Hardware Enclave Sandbox\",\n    client: \"Preview Client Enclave\",\n    phase: \"Phase III: Agent Alignment\",\n    status: \"On Track\",\n    owner: \"Dr. Sarah Vance\",\n    nodesCount: 6,\n    enclaveType: \"Intel SGX\",\n    desc: \"Transient isolated telemetry loop monitoring real-time agent handshakes and cryptographic state estimation bounds.\",\n    lastUpdated: new Date().toISOString()\n  };\n\n  // State\n  const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState<\"architecture\" | \"compliance\" | \"resources\">(\"architecture\");\n  const [isTelemetryLive, setIsTelemetryLive] = useState(true);\n  const [isAttesting, setIsAttesting] = useState(false);\n  const [attestationStatus, setAttestationStatus] = useState<\"idle\" | \"attesting\" | \"success\" | \"error\">(\"idle\");\n  const [logs, setLogs] = useState<string[]>([]);\n  const [attestationCounter, setAttestationCounter] = useState(0);\n\n  // Generate logs simulation\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const baseLogs = [\n      `[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] INITIATING HARDWARE ROOT HANDSHAKE ON ${project.enclaveType.toUpperCase()}...`,\n      `[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] ZERO-TRUST ATTESTATION: STABLE SHA-256 PARITY VERIFIED.`,\n      `[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] eBPF KERNEL DETECTOR: ACTIVE ON ${project.nodesCount} CLUSTER NODES.`,\n      `[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] REGISTRY STATUS: RESOLVED [${project.status.toUpperCase()}]`\n    ];\n    setLogs(baseLogs);\n  }, [project]);\n\n  // Simulate incoming live telemetry logs if live\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (!isTelemetryLive) return;\n\n    const interval = setInterval(() => {\n      const logTemplates = [\n        `[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] [TELEMETRY] Node cluster ${project.id}-node-${Math.floor(Math.random() * project.nodesCount) + 1} synchronized in 0.4ms.`,\n        `[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] [SECURITY] Guardrail execution audit: NO RULES BROKEN (Policy v4.2).`,\n        `[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] [METRIC] Isolation boundary overhead: CPU 0.05%, Secure Memory stable.`,\n        `[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] [ATTESTATION] Decoupled state cache signature verified: ${Math.random().toString(16).substring(2, 10).toUpperCase()}`,\n        `[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] [KERNEL] Event channel received event hook: eBPF hook resolved.`\n      ];\n      const randomLog = logTemplates[Math.floor(Math.random() * logTemplates.length)];\n      setLogs(prev => [randomLog, ...prev.slice(0, 15)]);\n    }, 4000);\n\n    return () => clearInterval(interval);\n  }, [isTelemetryLive, project]);\n\n  const triggerAttestation = () => {\n    if (isAttesting) return;\n    setIsAttesting(true);\n    setAttestationStatus(\"attesting\");\n    \n    // Add logs\n    setLogs(prev => [\n      `[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] [ATTEST] --> TRACE ROOT: Requesting hardware-level cryptographic key attestation...`,\n      ...prev\n    ]);\n\n    setTimeout(() => {\n      setLogs(prev => [\n        `[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] [ATTEST] --> PARITY MATCH: Intel/AMD secure token valid. Non-volatile register verification: 100%.`,\n        `[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] [ATTEST] --> DECOUPLED STATE: Hardware signature certified and sealed.`,\n        ...prev\n      ]);\n      setAttestationStatus(\"success\");\n      setIsAttesting(false);\n      setAttestationCounter(c => c + 1);\n\n      // Reset state back to idle after a while\n      setTimeout(() => setAttestationStatus(\"idle\"), 4000);\n    }, 2000);\n  };\n\n  const getStatusBadgeStyles = (status: string) => {\n    switch (status) {\n      case \"On Track\":\n        return \"bg-emerald-500/10 border-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400\";\n      case \"At Risk\":\n        return \"bg-amber-500/10 border-amber-500/20 text-amber-400\";\n      case \"Delayed\":\n        return \"bg-rose-500/10 border-rose-500/20 text-rose-400\";\n      case \"Paused\":\n        return \"bg-purple-500/10 border-purple-500/20 text-purple-400\";\n      default:\n        return \"bg-white/5 border-white/10 text-white/60\";\n    }\n  };\n\n  // Check which phase index we are currently on\n  const activePhaseIndex = PHASES_LIST.findIndex(p => p.startsWith(project.phase.split(\":\")[0]));\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"space-y-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-1 sm:px-4\">\n      {/* 1. Header with Breadcrumbs & Action Links */}\n      <div className=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-4 border-b border-white/5 pb-5\">\n        <div className=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n          <button\n            onClick={() => router.push(\"/admin/projects\")}\n            className=\"mt-1 p-2 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] text-white/50 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/[0.03] hover:border-white/10 cursor-pointer transition-all flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\"\n            title=\"Return to projects ledger\"\n            aria-label=\"Back to projects\"\n          >\n            <ArrowLeft className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n          </button>\n          <div>\n            <div className=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2\">\n              <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-bold text-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/5 border border-[#009DFF]/15 px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                Sovereign Administrative Oversight\n              </span>\n              <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-bold text-emerald-400 bg-emerald-500/5 border border-emerald-500/15 px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                {project.enclaveType} Enclave Isolated\n              </span>\n            </div>\n            <h2 className=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight font-mono uppercase mt-1.5 flex items-center gap-2\">\n              <span>{project.name}</span>\n              <span className=\"text-white/30 text-sm font-normal\">({project.id})</span>\n            </h2>\n            <p className=\"text-xs text-white/50 mt-1 max-w-2xl font-mono leading-relaxed\">\n              Oversight dashboard representing hardware telemetry, continuous verification parameters, and sandbox configurations.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        {/* Quick Back-to-List Actions */}\n        <div className=\"shrink-0 flex items-center gap-3\">\n          <Link\n            href=\"/admin/projects\"\n            className=\"h-9 px-4 rounded border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 bg-white/[0.01] text-[10.5px] font-mono font-bold text-white/70 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/[0.03] transition-all uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center gap-1.5\"\n          >\n            <span>Back to Registry</span>\n          </Link>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* 2. Top Stats Row (Project specific) */}\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4\">\n        <div className=\"border border-white/5 rounded-xl bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 space-y-1 relative overflow-hidden\">\n          <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between text-white/40 font-mono text-[9.5px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">\n            <span>Sovereign Client</span>\n            <Briefcase className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-white/25\" />\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"text-sm font-mono font-bold text-white truncate mt-1\">\n            {project.client.replace(\" [Preview Client]\", \"\")}\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/45 truncate\">Isolated Client Instance</div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div className=\"border border-white/5 rounded-xl bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 space-y-1 relative overflow-hidden\">\n          <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between text-white/40 font-mono text-[9.5px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">\n            <span>Active Enclave Nodes</span>\n            <Network className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#00FFC2]\" />\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"text-lg font-mono font-bold text-[#00FFC2] mt-1 flex items-baseline gap-1\">\n            <span>{project.nodesCount} Nodes</span>\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] text-[#00FFC2]/50 font-normal\">({project.enclaveType})</span>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/45 truncate\">Hardware execution spaces</div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div className=\"border border-white/5 rounded-xl bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 space-y-1 relative overflow-hidden\">\n          <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between text-white/40 font-mono text-[9.5px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">\n            <span>SLA Delivery Status</span>\n            <Activity className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"mt-1\">\n            <span className={`inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-[10px] font-mono font-bold ${getStatusBadgeStyles(project.status)}`}>\n              <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-current animate-pulse\" />\n              <span>{project.status.toUpperCase()}</span>\n            </span>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/45 mt-1 truncate\">Current compliance health index</div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div className=\"border border-white/5 rounded-xl bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm p-4 space-y-1 relative overflow-hidden\">\n          <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between text-white/40 font-mono text-[9.5px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">\n            <span>Audit & Owner Clearance</span>\n            <User className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-purple-400\" />\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"text-sm font-mono font-bold text-white truncate mt-1\">\n            {project.owner}\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-purple-400 font-bold truncate\">CLEARANCE LEVEL V SECURE</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* 3. Narrative Dynamic Phase Timeline */}\n      <div className=\"p-5 border border-white/5 bg-[#030303]/40 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl space-y-4\">\n        <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n            <Clock className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n            <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">Sovereign Lifecycle Alignment Sequence</h3>\n          </div>\n          <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono text-white/40\">\n            Active: <strong className=\"text-white font-mono\">{project.phase}</strong>\n          </span>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Timeline Visual Progress Stepper */}\n        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-5 gap-3 pt-2\">\n          {PHASES_LIST.map((phaseName, index) => {\n            const isCompleted = index < activePhaseIndex;\n            const isCurrent = index === activePhaseIndex;\n            const isPending = index > activePhaseIndex;\n\n            let indicatorBorder = \"border-white/10 text-white/35\";\n            let indicatorBg = \"bg-white/[0.01]\";\n            let textColor = \"text-white/30\";\n            let label = \"PENDING STEP\";\n\n            if (isCompleted) {\n              indicatorBorder = \"border-[#00FFC2]/30 text-[#00FFC2]\";\n              indicatorBg = \"bg-[#00FFC2]/5\";\n              textColor = \"text-[#00FFC2]/80\";\n              label = \"VERIFIED COMPLETED\";\n            } else if (isCurrent) {\n              if (project.status === \"At Risk\" || project.status === \"Delayed\") {\n                indicatorBorder = \"border-rose-500/40 text-rose-400 animate-pulse\";\n                indicatorBg = \"bg-rose-500/5\";\n                textColor = \"text-rose-400\";\n                label = \"ACTIVE UNDER REVIEW\";\n              } else {\n                indicatorBorder = \"border-[#009DFF]/40 text-[#009DFF]\";\n                indicatorBg = \"bg-[#009DFF]/5 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,157,255,0.1)]\";\n                textColor = \"text-white\";\n                label = \"ACTIVE LIVE TARGET\";\n              }\n            }\n\n            return (\n              <div \n                key={phaseName} \n                className={`p-3 rounded-lg border ${isCurrent ? \"border-white/15 bg-white/[0.02]\" : \"border-white/5 bg-transparent\"} flex flex-col justify-between space-y-3 transition-all`}\n              >\n                <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono font-bold text-white/30\">STEP 0{index + 1}</span>\n                  <span className={`text-[8px] font-mono font-bold uppercase px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded ${isCompleted ? \"bg-[#00FFC2]/10 text-[#00FFC2]\" : isCurrent ? \"bg-[#009DFF]/10 text-[#009DFF]\" : \"bg-white/5 text-white/30\"}`}>\n                    {isCompleted ? \"COMPLETED\" : isCurrent ? \"CURRENT\" : \"QUEUED\"}\n                  </span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div>\n                  <h4 className={`text-[11px] font-mono font-bold ${textColor} tracking-tight leading-tight`}>\n                    {phaseName.split(\": \").pop()}\n                  </h4>\n                  <span className=\"text-[8.5px] font-mono text-white/20 uppercase mt-1 block\">\n                    {label}\n                  </span>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Micro SVG progress pipeline connector */}\n                <div className=\"w-full h-1 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden relative\">\n                  <div \n                    className={`absolute inset-y-0 left-0 rounded-full transition-all duration-1000 ${\n                      isCompleted ? \"w-full bg-[#00FFC2]\" : isCurrent ? \"w-1/2 bg-[#009DFF]\" : \"w-0\"\n                    }`} \n                  />\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            );\n          })}\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* 4. Split Dashboard Panel Layout */}\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\n        \n        {/* Left Column (2/3 width) - Tabbed Spec System & Console Logs */}\n        <div className=\"lg:col-span-2 space-y-6\">\n          <div className=\"border border-white/5 rounded-xl bg-[#020202]/40 backdrop-blur-sm overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.4)]\">\n            \n            {/* Tabs Selector Bar */}\n            <div className=\"flex border-b border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01]\">\n              <button\n                onClick={() => setActiveTab(\"architecture\")}\n                className={`flex-1 py-3 px-4 text-center font-mono text-[10.5px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider border-b-2 transition-all cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center gap-2 ${\n                  activeTab === \"architecture\" \n                    ? \"text-[#009DFF] border-[#009DFF] bg-white/[0.01]\" \n                    : \"text-white/40 border-transparent hover:text-white/60 hover:bg-white/[0.005]\"\n                }`}\n              >\n                <Server className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n                <span>Enclave Clusters</span>\n              </button>\n              <button\n                onClick={() => setActiveTab(\"compliance\")}\n                className={`flex-1 py-3 px-4 text-center font-mono text-[10.5px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider border-b-2 transition-all cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center gap-2 ${\n                  activeTab === \"compliance\" \n                    ? \"text-[#009DFF] border-[#009DFF] bg-white/[0.01]\" \n                    : \"text-white/40 border-transparent hover:text-white/60 hover:bg-white/[0.005]\"\n                }`}\n              >\n                <ShieldCheck className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n                <span>Alignment Ledger</span>\n              </button>\n              <button\n                onClick={() => setActiveTab(\"resources\")}\n                className={`flex-1 py-3 px-4 text-center font-mono text-[10.5px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider border-b-2 transition-all cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center gap-2 ${\n                  activeTab === \"resources\" \n                    ? \"text-[#009DFF] border-[#009DFF] bg-white/[0.01]\" \n                    : \"text-white/40 border-transparent hover:text-white/60 hover:bg-white/[0.005]\"\n                }`}\n              >\n                <Sliders className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n                <span>Hardware Allocations</span>\n              </button>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Tab 1: Architecture Graphic + Telemetry Terminal */}\n            {activeTab === \"architecture\" && (\n              <div className=\"p-5 space-y-5 animate-in fade-in duration-200\">\n                <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                  <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">Secure Isolation Topology</h3>\n                  <p className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-white/50 leading-relaxed\">\n                    Visual simulation representational diagram of the active {project.nodesCount}-node airgapped hardware enclave. High-velocity TLS loops feed runtime alignment telemetry.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* SVG/CSS Cluster Diagram Graphic */}\n                <div className=\"relative py-8 px-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#040404]/80 flex flex-col items-center justify-center overflow-hidden min-h-[220px]\">\n                  \n                  {/* Decorative background grids */}\n                  <div className=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,rgba(255,255,255,0.02)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,rgba(255,255,255,0.02)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:14px_24px] pointer-events-none\" />\n                  \n                  <div className=\"relative z-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 max-w-lg\">\n                    {/* Render node visual representation */}\n                    {Array.from({ length: project.nodesCount }).map((_, nodeIdx) => (\n                      <div key={nodeIdx} className=\"flex flex-col items-center space-y-1.5 relative group\">\n                        \n                        {/* Connecting Line effect between nodes using CSS */}\n                        {nodeIdx > 0 && (\n                          <div className=\"absolute right-full top-5 w-6 h-[1px] bg-[#009DFF]/20 group-hover:bg-[#009DFF]/40 transition-colors hidden sm:block\" />\n                        )}\n\n                        <div className={`w-10 h-10 rounded-lg border flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 relative ${\n                          !isTelemetryLive \n                            ? \"border-white/10 bg-white/5 text-white/40\" \n                            : project.status === \"On Track\" \n                              ? \"border-emerald-500/20 bg-emerald-500/5 text-emerald-400 shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(16,185,129,0.08)] hover:border-emerald-500/40\" \n                              : project.status === \"Paused\"\n                                ? \"border-purple-500/20 bg-purple-500/5 text-purple-400 shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(168,85,247,0.08)]\"\n                                : \"border-rose-500/20 bg-rose-500/5 text-rose-400 shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(244,63,94,0.08)] animate-pulse\"\n                        }`}>\n                          <Cpu className=\"w-4.5 h-4.5\" />\n                          \n                          {/* Pulsing state ring for active enclaves */}\n                          {isTelemetryLive && (\n                            <span className={`absolute -inset-0.5 rounded-lg border animate-ping opacity-25 ${\n                              project.status === \"On Track\" ? \"border-emerald-400\" : project.status === \"Paused\" ? \"border-purple-400\" : \"border-rose-400\"\n                            }`} style={{ animationDuration: `${2.5 + nodeIdx * 0.5}s` }} />\n                          )}\n                        </div>\n                        <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-bold text-white/40 group-hover:text-white/60 transition-colors\">\n                          N-0{nodeIdx + 1}\n                        </span>\n                      </div>\n                    ))}\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Operational Telemetry Banner inside topology */}\n                  <div className=\"absolute bottom-3 left-3 flex items-center gap-2 text-[9.5px] font-mono px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-black/60 border border-white/5\">\n                    <span className={`w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full ${isTelemetryLive ? \"bg-[#00FFC2] animate-pulse\" : \"bg-white/20\"}`} />\n                    <span className=\"text-white/50\">\n                      Telemetry Pipeline State: <strong className={isTelemetryLive ? \"text-[#00FFC2]\" : \"text-white/30\"}>{isTelemetryLive ? \"ONLINE (VERIFIED)\" : \"PAUSED\"}</strong>\n                    </span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Real-time Telemetry Event Log Stream Terminal */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                      <Terminal className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-white/30\" />\n                      <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">Live eBPF Kernel Audits</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                      <button \n                        onClick={() => setLogs(prev => [`[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] [SYSTEM] Terminal log logs scrubbed.`, ...prev.slice(0, 1)])}\n                        className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/35 hover:text-white transition-colors cursor-pointer\"\n                      >\n                        Clear Terminal\n                      </button>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl bg-black border border-white/5 font-mono text-[10.5px] leading-relaxed text-white/70 h-44 overflow-y-auto space-y-1.5 scrollbar-thin select-all\">\n                    {logs.map((logStr, logIdx) => {\n                      let logColor = \"text-white/60\";\n                      if (logStr.includes(\"[SECURITY]\")) logColor = \"text-[#00FFC2]\";\n                      else if (logStr.includes(\"[METRIC]\")) logColor = \"text-purple-300\";\n                      else if (logStr.includes(\"[ATTESTATION]\") || logStr.includes(\"[ATTEST]\")) logColor = \"text-[#009DFF]\";\n                      else if (logStr.includes(\"ERROR\") || logStr.includes(\"RISK\")) logColor = \"text-rose-400\";\n                      \n                      return (\n                        <div key={logIdx} className={`${logColor} hover:bg-white/[0.02] px-1 rounded transition-colors`}>\n                          {logStr}\n                        </div>\n                      );\n                    })}\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            )}\n\n            {/* Tab 2: Compliance Policy Ledger */}\n            {activeTab === \"compliance\" && (\n              <div className=\"p-5 space-y-4 animate-in fade-in duration-200\">\n                <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                  <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">Continuous Verification Policy Ruleset</h3>\n                  <p className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-white/50\">\n                    The platform continuously executes isolated preflight assertion loops. Below is the active policy alignment state for the hardware enclave cluster.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n\n                <div className=\"space-y-2.5\">\n                  {[\n                    { id: \"POL-001\", name: \"ISO-27001 SOC2 Hardware Handshake Verification\", desc: \"Verifies root credentials baked inside silicon secure enclave directly.\", pass: true, detail: \"Attestation Token parity: OK\" },\n                    { id: \"POL-002\", name: \"Dynamic Prompt Injection Filter\", desc: \"Filters input streams for extreme model jailbreak attacks in sandbox state.\", pass: project.status !== \"At Risk\", detail: project.status === \"At Risk\" ? \"WARNING: Latency overhead high\" : \"Latency threshold: 0.8ms\" },\n                    { id: \"POL-003\", name: \"eBPF Event Logger Trace Integrity Check\", desc: \"Ensures kernel hooks have not been decoupled or memory sniffed.\", pass: true, detail: \"Kernel hook: active\" },\n                    { id: \"POL-004\", name: \"TLS 1.3 Ephemeral Cryptographic Key Socket\", desc: \"Dual-socket airgapped connection parameters with external lattices.\", pass: project.status !== \"Delayed\", detail: project.status === \"Delayed\" ? \"DELAYED: Ephemeral socket retry\" : \"Established secure tunnel\" },\n                    { id: \"POL-005\", name: \"Sovereign Alignment Core Guardrail Execution\", desc: \"Evaluates token compliance against the customized regulatory guidelines.\", pass: true, detail: \"Rules evaluated: 42/42\" }\n                  ].map((rule) => (\n                    <div key={rule.id} className=\"p-3 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-black/40 flex items-start justify-between gap-3 font-mono\">\n                      <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                          <span className=\"text-[8.5px] font-bold text-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/10 border border-[#009DFF]/20 px-1 rounded\">\n                            {rule.id}\n                          </span>\n                          <h4 className=\"text-[11px] font-bold text-white\">{rule.name}</h4>\n                        </div>\n                        <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/45 leading-relaxed\">{rule.desc}</p>\n                        <div className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/30\">Trace status: <span className=\"text-white/60\">{rule.detail}</span></div>\n                      </div>\n\n                      <div className=\"shrink-0 pt-0.5\">\n                        {rule.pass ? (\n                          <span className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[9.5px] font-bold text-emerald-400 bg-emerald-500/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-emerald-500/20\">\n                            <CheckCircle2 className=\"w-3 h-3\" />\n                            <span>PASSED</span>\n                          </span>\n                        ) : (\n                          <span className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[9.5px] font-bold text-rose-400 bg-rose-500/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded border border-rose-500/20\">\n                            <AlertTriangle className=\"w-3 h-3 animate-pulse\" />\n                            <span>ALERT</span>\n                          </span>\n                        )}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  ))}\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            )}\n\n            {/* Tab 3: Ephemeral Resource Allocations */}\n            {activeTab === \"resources\" && (\n              <div className=\"p-5 space-y-5 animate-in fade-in duration-200\">\n                <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                  <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">Silicon Resource Allocation Metrics</h3>\n                  <p className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-white/50\">\n                    Sovereign airgapped workloads execute on dedicated secure hardware. Below is the physical sandbox partition telemetry.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n\n                <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n                  {/* Metric Progress 1 */}\n                  <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/30 space-y-3 font-mono\">\n                    <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-[10.5px]\">\n                      <span className=\"text-white/40 uppercase\">Secure Page Memory Ring</span>\n                      <span className=\"text-emerald-400 font-bold\">42.8 GB / 64.0 GB</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"h-2 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden\">\n                      <div className=\"h-full bg-emerald-400 rounded-full transition-all duration-1000\" style={{ width: \"66.8%\" }} />\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"text-[9px] text-white/30 flex justify-between\">\n                      <span>SGX EPC MEMORY ENVELOPE</span>\n                      <span>66.8% ALLOCATED</span>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Metric Progress 2 */}\n                  <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/30 space-y-3 font-mono\">\n                    <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-[10.5px]\">\n                      <span className=\"text-white/40 uppercase\">Host Context State Cache</span>\n                      <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-bold\">12.5 MB / 16.0 MB</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"h-2 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden\">\n                      <div className=\"h-full bg-[#009DFF] rounded-full transition-all duration-1000\" style={{ width: \"78.1%\" }} />\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"text-[9px] text-white/30 flex justify-between\">\n                      <span>DECOUPLED CONTEXT BUFFER</span>\n                      <span>78.1% CACHE USAGE</span>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Metric Progress 3 */}\n                  <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/30 space-y-3 font-mono\">\n                    <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-[10.5px]\">\n                      <span className=\"text-white/40 uppercase\">Processor Threads Peak Load</span>\n                      <span className={`font-bold ${project.status === \"At Risk\" ? \"text-rose-400\" : \"text-purple-400\"}`}>\n                        {project.status === \"At Risk\" ? \"91.2%\" : \"24.5%\"} CPU Load\n                      </span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"h-2 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden\">\n                      <div \n                        className={`h-full rounded-full transition-all duration-1000 ${project.status === \"At Risk\" ? \"bg-rose-500\" : \"bg-purple-500\"}`} \n                        style={{ width: project.status === \"At Risk\" ? \"91.2%\" : \"24.5%\" }} \n                      />\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"text-[9px] text-white/30 flex justify-between\">\n                      <span>{project.nodesCount * 4} PHYSICAL CORES ASSIGNED</span>\n                      <span>REAL-TIME DECOUPLED AUDIT</span>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Physical Specs list */}\n                  <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/30 flex flex-col justify-between font-mono text-[10px] space-y-1.5 text-white/70\">\n                    <div className=\"flex justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-1.5\">\n                      <span className=\"text-white/40\">Hardware Root Lock:</span>\n                      <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">SEALED (NIST SP800)</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"flex justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-1.5\">\n                      <span className=\"text-white/40\">Encryption Loop:</span>\n                      <span className=\"text-[#00FFC2] font-bold\">AES-256-XTS</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"flex justify-between pt-0.5\">\n                      <span className=\"text-white/40\">State Storage Parity:</span>\n                      <span className=\"text-white\">Transient Isolation Only</span>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            )}\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Right Column (1/3 width) - Quick Actions & Team Ownership details */}\n        <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n          \n          {/* Quick Actions Panel */}\n          <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-4 shadow-[0_4px_25px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)]\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n              <Settings className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n              <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">Administrative Controls</h3>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"space-y-2.5 font-mono\">\n              \n              {/* Action 1: Toggle Telemetry Flow */}\n              <button\n                onClick={() => {\n                  setIsTelemetryLive(!isTelemetryLive);\n                  setLogs(prev => [\n                    `[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] [USER_CMD] Telemetry stream manually ${!isTelemetryLive ? \"ENABLED\" : \"PAUSED\"}.`,\n                    ...prev\n                  ]);\n                }}\n                className={`w-full h-10 px-3 rounded-lg border text-[11px] font-bold uppercase transition-all flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer ${\n                  isTelemetryLive \n                    ? \"border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-500/5 text-amber-400 hover:bg-amber-500/10\" \n                    : \"border-emerald-500/30 bg-emerald-500/5 text-emerald-400 hover:bg-emerald-500/10\"\n                }`}\n              >\n                <span className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                  {isTelemetryLive ? <Square className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" /> : <Play className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />}\n                  <span>{isTelemetryLive ? \"Pause Telemetry Flow\" : \"Resume Telemetry Flow\"}</span>\n                </span>\n                <span className=\"text-[8.5px] px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-black/60 rounded border border-white/5 font-mono\">\n                  {isTelemetryLive ? \"ACTIVE\" : \"PAUSED\"}\n                </span>\n              </button>\n\n              {/* Action 2: Trigger Attestation */}\n              <button\n                onClick={triggerAttestation}\n                disabled={isAttesting}\n                className={`w-full h-10 px-3 rounded-lg border text-[11px] font-bold uppercase transition-all flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer ${\n                  isAttesting \n                    ? \"border-white/10 bg-white/5 text-white/40 cursor-wait\" \n                    : \"border-[#009DFF]/30 bg-[#009DFF]/5 text-[#009DFF] hover:bg-[#009DFF]/10 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,157,255,0.03)]\"\n                }`}\n              >\n                <span className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                  <RefreshCw className={`w-3.5 h-3.5 ${isAttesting ? \"animate-spin text-[#009DFF]\" : \"\"}`} />\n                  <span>{isAttesting ? \"Attesting Hardware...\" : \"Re-Attest Cluster\"}</span>\n                </span>\n                <span className=\"text-[8.5px] px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-black/60 rounded border border-white/5 font-mono\">\n                  {attestationCounter > 0 ? `VERIFIED x${attestationCounter}` : \"SEALED\"}\n                </span>\n              </button>\n\n              {/* Attestation Notification Banner */}\n              {attestationStatus === \"success\" && (\n                <div className=\"p-2.5 rounded border border-emerald-500/25 bg-emerald-500/5 text-[#00FFC2] text-[10px] leading-relaxed flex items-start gap-1.5 animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-top-2 duration-300\">\n                  <CheckCircle2 className=\"w-4 h-4 text-emerald-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" />\n                  <span>Success: Dynamic Hardware Attestation verified. Root key authenticated against NIST repository.</span>\n                </div>\n              )}\n\n              {/* Policy Enforcement Warning Panel for At Risk / Delayed */}\n              {(project.status === \"At Risk\" || project.status === \"Delayed\") && (\n                <div className=\"p-3 rounded border border-rose-500/25 bg-rose-500/5 text-rose-400 text-[10px] leading-relaxed space-y-2 animate-in fade-in duration-300\">\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                    <ShieldAlert className=\"w-4 h-4 shrink-0\" />\n                    <span>SLA Risk Flag Active</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <p className=\"text-white/60 text-[9.5px]\">\n                    Continuous governance loops are reporting state drift. Recommended: Force a hardware cluster re-attestation or coordinate alignment hooks with owner.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              )}\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Secure Ownership & Auditor Context Card */}\n          <div className=\"p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-4 shadow-[0_4px_25px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)] font-mono\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n              <Lock className=\"w-4 h-4 text-purple-400\" />\n              <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider\">Authorized Custodian</h3>\n            </div>\n\n            <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n                <div className=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-purple-500/10 border border-purple-500/20 text-[#009DFF] flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm\">\n                  {project.owner.split(\" \").pop()?.substring(0, 2).toUpperCase() || \"CN\"}\n                </div>\n                <div>\n                  <h4 className=\"text-[12px] font-bold text-white leading-none\">{project.owner}</h4>\n                  <span className=\"text-[9.5px] text-purple-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider block mt-1\">SLA Execution Lead</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"space-y-2 text-[10px] text-white/50 pt-1 border-t border-white/5\">\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                  <span>Duty Email:</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-white/80\">{project.owner.toLowerCase().replace(\"dr. \", \"\").replace(\" \", \".\")}@governance.gff.ai</span>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                  <span>Cryptographic Key ID:</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-white/80\">0xDF741AA8</span>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n                  <span>Epoch Last Signed:</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-white/80\">2026-06-27T15:00</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <p className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/30 leading-normal bg-black/30 p-2.5 rounded border border-white/5\">\n                Custodians execute compliance oversight overrides. Active keys expire automatically after a 12-hour session window.\n              </p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  );\n}"}}}
